text: Régis Juanico (born 5 February 1972 in Saint-Rémy, Saône-et-Loire) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents Loire's 1st constituency, and is a member of Génération.s and former member of the Socialist Party. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:People from Saint-Rémy, Saône-et-Loire Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Politicians from Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes Category:Pantheon-Sorbonne University alumni
